    Invoice class prints out the receipt with billing, shipping information, and contact information.

    ShoppingApp class has option to open new and previous StoreApp and ShoppingCart.

    ShoppingCart class has a shopping cart with item and item quantity.

    StoreApp class has all the items and a link to shopping cart.
